snippet.title: These Celebrities Defended Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard! (REWARDED)
snippet.description:
These Celebrities Defended Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard! (REWARDED)

There shouldn't be a single person in the world not to know all the drama that has been going on between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. If you hadn't, Amber suddenly accused Johnny of 15 cases of violence. But, It seems like her accusations were never really based since not only fans, but also Celebrities have shown support to Johnny Depp speaking out against Amber Heard.
